machine_start_gcode.default_value:
; Start code dual extruder
M572 D0 S0.09		; Set or report extruder pressure advance, Extruder 0, Pressure advance amount 0.03
M572 D1 S0.09		; Set or report extruder pressure advance, Extruder 1, Pressure advance amount 0.03
G21			; Set Units to Millimeters
G90			; Set to Absolute Positioning
M82			; Set extruder to absolute mode
M107			; Fan Off
G28			; Return to home 
G1 Z15.0 F150  		; Linear Move to Z=0, rate = 150mm/min 
T0			; Select tool 0
G92 E0			; Program absolute extruder position to 0
G1 X30 Y-2 F800		; Linear Move to X=  30mm, Y = -2mm, rate = 800mm/min 
G1 Z0.35 F200 		; Linear Move to Z=0.35, feedrate = 200mm/min
G1 X85 Y-2 E13 F200		; Linear Move to X= 85 mm, Y = -2mm, feedrate = 200mm/min, extrude 13mm filament
G1 E15 F200			; Extrude feedrate = 200mm/min, extrude 13mm filament
G1 Z5 F200			; Linear Move to Z= 5mm, feedrate = 200mm/min 
G92 E0			; Program absolute extruder position to 0
G0  E-1 F200		; Non print move, Retract material
T1			; Select tool 1
G92 E0			; Program absolute extruder position to 0
G1 X210 Y-2 F800		; Linear Move to X=  210mm, Y = -2mm, feedrate = 800mm/min 
G1 Z0.35 F200		; Linear Move to Z=0.35, feedrate = 200mm/min
G1 X275 Y-2 E13 F200		; Linear Move to X= 275mm, Y = -2mm, feedrate = 200mm/min, extrude 13mm filament
G1 E15 F200			;  Extrude feedrate = 200mm/min, extrude 13mm filament
G1 Z5 F200			; Linear Move to Z=   5mm, feedrate = 200mm/min
G92 E0			; Program absolute extruder position to 0
G0 E-1 F200			; Non print move,  retract material
T0			; Select tool 0
G1 F150			; Linear Move feedrate = 200mm/min
M117 Printing...

machine_end_gcode.default_value:
; End code dual extruder
M1002			; Beginning of End GCode.
M221 T0 S100		; Set extrude factor override percentage, extruder 0, extrude override factor 100%
M221 T1 S100		; Set extrude factor override percentage, extruder 1, extrude override factor 100%
M104 T0 S0		; Set Extruder 0 Temperature to 0C
M104 T1 S0		; Set Extruder 1 Temperature to 0C
M106 P2 S0		; Cooling fan On for fan 2, fan speed 0
M140 S0			; Set Bed Temperature (Fast) to 0C
M117 Print Complete.		; Display Message "Print Complete."
M107			; Fan Off
G91			; Set to Relative Positioning
G1 E-1 F300			; Retract 1 mm 
G1 Z+0.5 E-5 Y-20 F9000.00	; Move .5 mm up, retract 5mm further 
G28 X0 U0			; Return to home 
M84			; Stop idle hold, disable steppers until next move 
G90			; Set to Absolute Positioning
